## Network & proxy

Symptoms: connection reset, timeouts, certificate errors, replica unreachable, deploy hangs.

```bash
curl -v https://ic0.app        # is the outside world reachable?
curl -v http://127.0.0.1:4943  # is the local replica reachable? (adjust port)
```

| Symptom | Likely cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| TLS/cert error on `curl https://ic0.app` | TLS-inspecting proxy injecting its own CA | Add the corporate CA to the system trust store and to `NODE_EXTRA_CA_CERTS` for the JS agent |
| Replica unreachable from Windows browser, fine inside WSL | WSL2 network namespace — replica bound to WSL's loopback | Bind the replica to `0.0.0.0`, or reach it via the WSL VM's IP; `localhost` is not shared |
| Everything hangs, including `curl` | Proxy env vars set but blocking loopback | Add `127.0.0.1,localhost` to `NO_PROXY` |
| DNS failures | Corporate DNS not resolving IC domains | `nslookup ic0.app`; escalate to network config |

If the network is the cause, **stop here.** Do not proceed to other branches.

